\viewkind4\uc1\pard\cf1\lang0\f0\fs20 We allow a 31-day grace period for payments of every premium after the first premium payment. A payment will be deemed made within the grace period if delivery of it to Us is made within the grace period. This Policy will remain in force during a grace period. If the Primary Insured dies during a grace period, We will deduct the premium for the Primary Insured\rquote s coverage under this Policy due for the grace period in computing the Death Benefit Amount.\par
